    "content": "<h1 id=\"user-guide\">User Guide<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#user-guide\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h1>\n<p>Learn how to get the most out of Chekameh.</p>\n<h2 id=\"navigating-the-site\">Navigating the Site<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#navigating-the-site\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<p>The site has four main sections:</p>\n<ol>\n<li><strong>Home</strong> — Project overview and introduction</li>\n<li><strong>Data</strong> — Poets, eras, cities, and poem collections</li>\n<li><strong>Technical</strong> — How the site was built</li>\n<li><strong>Resources</strong> — Guides, FAQ, and contribution info</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"using-the-interactive-map\">Using the Interactive Map<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#using-the-interactive-map\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<!-- Detailed map guide to be added -->\n\n<p>The map shows literary centers across the Persian-speaking world. Features include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Zoom and pan to explore regions</li>\n<li>Click cities for poet information</li>\n<li>Filter by era using the timeline</li>\n<li>Search for specific poets or locations</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"timeline-feature\">Timeline Feature<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#timeline-feature\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<!-- Timeline guide to be added -->\n\n<p>Slide through centuries to see when poets were active. The timeline syncs with the map.</p>\n<h2 id=\"poet-profiles\">Poet Profiles<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#poet-profiles\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<!-- Profile guide to be added -->\n\n<p>Each poet page includes biographical info, major works, and connections.</p>\n<h2 id=\"search\">Search<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#search\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<!-- Search guide to be added -->\n\n<p>Find poets by name, era, location, or keywords.</p>\n<h2 id=\"language-switching\">Language Switching<a class=\"headerlink\" href=\"#language-switching\" title=\"Permanent link\">&para;</a></h2>\n<p>Use the language toggle in the navigation bar to switch between English and Persian. Content is available in both languages.</p>\n<hr />\n<p><em>More detailed guides coming soon.</em></p>",
